      <h1 class="font-display font-extrabold text-white leading-tight max-w-2xl">Contact Barnt Green Cattery</h1>
      <p class="mt-5 text-white/80 text-lg max-w-xl leading-relaxed">We are ideally located in the Birmingham countryside, close to Bromsgrove and Redditch. Get in touch to check availability or arrange a viewing.</p>
